<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4A90E2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Community!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
        <p>We're thrilled to have you on board! You have successfully signed up for our application.</p>
        <p>This is just the beginning of our journey together. We'll send you more information shortly to help you get started and make the most of our features.</p>
        <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore and let us know if you have any questions.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2026 Internship Tutorial. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
